09. Officers being promoted under this order not to appear at the place of appointment on promotion.

In the event of attempts to make appointments elsewhere, either under royal pressure or otherwise, a confidential report from the relevant authorities will be recorded accordingly. It should also be noted that disciplinary action will be taken against the officer concerned as the act of coercion violates Rules 3 (3) and 23 of the Maharashtra Civil Services (Conduct) Rules, 1979.
